-940x1273.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-02-800x1083.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-02-768x1040.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-02-1135x1536.jpg 1135w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-02-1513x2048.jpg 1513w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1891px) 100vw, 1891px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLocated on a quiet suburban street in Wanaka, New Zealand, the compact home is defined by a simple gable form and a sturdy black rain screen.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2446\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-03.jpg\" alt=\"A small one bedroom home with an exterior of asphalt shingles and larch weatherboards.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-03-940x1198.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-03-800x1019.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-03-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-03-1206x1536.jpg 1206w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-03-1608x2048.jpg 1608w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe external cladding is restrained but functional, combining asphalt shingles and larch weatherboards.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1838\"