www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-05-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-05-1206x1536.jpg 1206w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eEven though the home is small, none of the essentials of a larger home are missing. The house has a full kitchen, bedroom area and living space. The double height volume with its glazed facade creates a sense of airiness and space. There is room for artwork, a full sized fridge, two large couches and a coffee table.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1270\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-07.jpg\" alt=\"A small one bedroom home with an open main floor and a loft bedroom.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-07.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-07-940x622.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-07-800x529.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-07-768x508.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-07-1536x1016.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe design concept was envisioned as a crafted joinery box with no wasted space. Spring-back drawers pull out of each step tread and more storage is concealed under the kitchen joinery in the toe space. The bathroom is located off the kitchen and the bedroom is located upstairs. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2156\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-08.jpg\" alt=\"A small one bedroom home with an open main floor and a loft bedroom.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-08.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-08-940x1267.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-08-800x1078.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-08-768x1035.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-08-1140x1536.jpg 1140w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/small-one-bedroom-house-110325-1108-08-1520x2048.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can watch a short video of the home here:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ciframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/265476317\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere’s a look at the architectural drawings for the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2224\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/tiny-house-architectural-drawing-110325-1104-01.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings for a small one bedroom home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/tiny-house-architectural-drawing-110325-1104-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/tiny-house-architectural-drawing-110325-1104-01-940x1089.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/tiny-house-architectural-drawing-110325-1104-01-800x927.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-c